name: Ultra NFT (Demo)
description:
NFT is becoming a new buzz in the world so naturally we on-boarded the idea. Hence Ultra NFT which is a Figma UI Kit related to NFT.


What you'll get

  • 12 Web Screens with Bootstrap Grid
  • Plethora of Components
  • Globally defined Colours & Typography
  • Access to Illustrations & Icons (Links available in Figma file)
